sections.tagline: I build scalable and dynamic web applications using cutting-edge technologies like JavaScript, Vue.js, React.js, Next.js, Node.js, and Laravel. From intuitive UIs to robust backends, I bring ideas to life.

sections.headline: About Me
sections.text: I’m Rocky Gonzales, a full-stack developer passionate about delivering high-performance web applications. I specialize in front-end frameworks like Vue.js, React.js, and Next.js, while building robust backends with Node.js and Laravel. I focus on writing clean, maintainable code and creating seamless user experiences.
